Name: Dodge It!
About the game: / Hello, let me introduce myself, my name is Samuel Crevier and I am 21 years old. I live in Canada in a city called Granby in Quebec. I created Dodge It! myself without the help of anyone. I just wanted to say to those who will download my game a big THANK YOU! HOW TO PLAY In this game you will need to collect the most black circle without being touch by the red circle if you touch them you will die instantly! every time you collect a black circle a new red circle appears.
